02:10.511 --> 02:11.877
Oh, my God.

02:11.878 --> 02:13.610
Kara, my darling!

02:13.611 --> 02:14.778
What did you do?

02:18.078 --> 02:20.077
No!

02:26.845 --> 02:28.744
No!

02:28.745 --> 02:30.411
Wh... Why?

02:46.345 --> 02:47.510
911 operator.

02:47.511 --> 02:48.544
Hello, police.

02:48.545 --> 02:49.777
Yes, ma'am.

02:49.778 --> 02:51.310
This is Kara Clayton.

02:51.311 --> 02:52.344
And what's your emergency?

02:52.345 --> 02:54.577
My husband tried to stab me to death.

02:54.578 --> 02:56.977
- Okay, ma'am.
- I shot him three times.

02:56.978 --> 02:59.177
I need you to stay on the line with me.

03:44.378 --> 03:46.844
Hey, where's Dr. Bull?

03:46.845 --> 03:48.377
Mm.

04:06.978 --> 04:08.010
Dr. Bull?

04:08.011 --> 04:09.711
They're ready to see you now.

04:11.045 --> 04:12.910
Dr. Bull, Perry Sinclair.

04:12.911 --> 04:14.644
- Hey.
- Thank you for joining us.

04:14.645 --> 04:16.510
Well, how could I resist?

04:16.809 --> 04:17.809
Look at this room.

04:17.810 --> 04:19.108
Who do we have here?

04:19.108 --> 04:21.075
This is George Donahue,

04:21.076 --> 04:22.742
Clayton Communications' COO.

04:22.743 --> 04:23.775
Doctor.

04:23.776 --> 04:24.890
It's an honor.

04:25.576 --> 04:27.108
And look at this.

04:27.109 --> 04:29.208
Six different law firms
represented here.

04:29.209 --> 04:31.308
It's like the New York Yankees
of attorneys.

04:31.309 --> 04:33.308
What happened? Bill Gates
run a traffic light?

04:34.676 --> 04:36.242
Have a seat, Dr. Bull.

04:36.243 --> 04:39.108
All right, but only
'cause you outnumber me.

04:40.976 --> 04:42.575
What can I do for you fellas?

04:42.576 --> 04:44.808
I think it's what we can
do for you, Dr. Bull.

04:44.809 --> 04:46.937
We'd like to offer you a job.

04:47.080 --> 04:49.308
You are a witness.

04:49.309 --> 04:51.191
And you have rights.

04:52.230 --> 04:56.062
The opposition lawyer
turns to you and says,

04:56.142 --> 04:58.308
"Let's assume
the following hypothetical."

04:58.476 --> 05:00.876
You have the right to say...

05:02.543 --> 05:03.708
Marissa in here?

05:03.709 --> 05:06.808
No, nope, nobody, just, uh, just me.

05:06.809 --> 05:09.460
Sorry.

05:13.409 --> 05:15.008
Hey, I've been looking

05:15.009 --> 05:16.708
all over for you.
What are you doing in here?

05:16.709 --> 05:19.942
Going over the books
where no one can see them.

05:19.943 --> 05:21.875
Oh, the books are great.

05:21.876 --> 05:24.275
The books are gonna be fine.

05:24.276 --> 05:25.775
Oh, my goodness.

05:25.776 --> 05:27.075
A quarter of a million dollars?

05:27.076 --> 05:29.742
Who gave you a check for
a quarter of a million dollars?

05:29.743 --> 05:32.008
The Clayton family estate.

05:32.009 --> 05:34.508
They're pressuring the DA
to try the young widow Clayton

05:34.509 --> 05:35.975
for the murder of her husband.

05:35.976 --> 05:37.854
Murder? Based on...

05:37.855 --> 05:39.328
Based on the fact that she shot him.

05:39.329 --> 05:40.875
A fact she does not dispute.

05:40.876 --> 05:42.675
- Can you say "money in the bank"?
- Okay.

05:42.676 --> 05:44.775
But according to the paper,
the late Mr. Clayton

05:44.776 --> 05:47.608
was attempting to slice and dice
his dearly beloved

05:47.609 --> 05:50.575
just prior to her deciding
to use him for target practice.

05:50.576 --> 05:52.175
I believe they call that "self-defense."

05:52.176 --> 05:54.275
Maybe. Or maybe she shot first

05:54.276 --> 05:56.175
and he stabbed her in self defense.

05:56.176 --> 05:57.642
Who cares?

05:57.643 --> 05:59.575
It's a quarter of a
million dollar retainer,

05:59.576 --> 06:02.275
and another quarter of a million
if we actually go to trial

06:02.276 --> 06:04.575
- and find Mrs. Clayton guilty.
- Wow.

06:04.576 --> 06:07.908
I had no idea the famous
Dr. Jason Bull can be bought.

06:07.909 --> 06:09.142
For a quarter of a million dollars,

06:09.143 --> 06:10.143
not only can I be bought,

06:10.144 --> 06:12.375
you can gift wrap me.

06:12.376 --> 06:14.008
Which reminds me,

06:14.009 --> 06:15.275
guess who's in town?

06:15.609 --> 06:17.942
I'm sorry, did I miss
a change of subject?

06:17.943 --> 06:21.351
The best un-wrapper in the world.

06:21.376 --> 06:24.426
Miss Diana Lindsay, attorney-at-law.

06:25.149 --> 06:26.782
Single woman at large.

06:26.919 --> 06:27.990
New York.

06:28.015 --> 06:29.384
What are you talking about?

06:29.409 --> 06:31.142
New Yorkers, they sound
just like everybody else.

06:31.143 --> 06:32.608
French.

06:32.609 --> 06:34.508
Do you come
to this ceiling often, monsieur?

06:34.509 --> 06:37.775
And now your hometown, Callisto, Texas.

06:37.776 --> 06:40.431
Callisto, Texas? All right.

06:40.432 --> 06:43.842
That fella Bull,
he's all hat and no cattle.

06:43.843 --> 06:45.875
That's not what you said 15 minutes ago.

06:45.876 --> 06:47.575
Well, I'm sorry, darling, but I lied.

06:47.576 --> 06:49.476
Mm, that's what I love about you.

06:50.109 --> 06:53.208
What? That I lie?

06:53.209 --> 06:55.642
No, that there are so many of you.

06:55.643 --> 06:58.875
It's like I can cheat on you with you.

06:58.876 --> 07:02.408
Well, I am glad you are in
such a good mood, Doctor.

07:02.409 --> 07:03.573
Mm.

07:04.076 --> 07:05.776
I need a favor.

07:06.709 --> 07:08.408
It's the reason I invited you over here.

07:09.843 --> 07:11.708
Stupid me, I thought
I'd already done the favor

07:11.709 --> 07:12.775
you invited me over here for.

07:12.776 --> 07:15.208
Hmm. Don't overestimate yourself.

07:15.209 --> 07:16.475
That was my favor to you.

07:16.476 --> 07:17.908
- Ah.
- Mm.

07:17.909 --> 07:18.876
Really?

07:18.877 --> 07:20.743
I need your help with something, Jason.

07:23.976 --> 07:25.675
You know, ever since I lost that case

07:25.676 --> 07:27.242
where the sky bridge fell down,
I've been looking for

07:27.243 --> 07:29.808
another high-profile
New York opportunity.

07:29.809 --> 07:30.809
Something to

07:30.810 --> 07:32.477
establish my name here.

07:33.395 --> 07:35.063
I think I found it.

07:36.643 --> 07:37.675
Kara Clayton.

07:37.676 --> 07:39.609
She's asked me to represent her.

07:40.284 --> 07:43.175
Her late husband's estate's been
putting all kinds of pressure

07:43.176 --> 07:44.775
on the DA to try her for murder.

07:44.776 --> 07:47.342
- You don't say.
- Well, the...

07:47.343 --> 07:50.208
publicity alone makes this
an opportunity of a lifetime.

07:50.209 --> 07:53.480
Not to mention the fact that
this is, uh, self-defense,

07:53.481 --> 07:54.880
pretty cut and dried.

07:54.881 --> 07:56.247
I hear the other side's already gone out

07:56.248 --> 07:57.580
and hired the biggest guns in town

07:57.581 --> 07:58.824
- to go after her.
- I know.

07:58.849 --> 07:59.849
Mm.

07:59.874 --> 08:01.580
That's why I like it.

08:01.581 --> 08:03.080
Diana versus Goliath.

08:03.081 --> 08:04.213
You know? Boys against the girls.

08:04.214 --> 08:05.247
What?

08:05.248 --> 08:08.221
Except... one boy.

08:08.648 --> 08:10.280
I want you on my team, Jason.

08:10.281 --> 08:14.247
I need you on my team.

08:16.214 --> 08:17.813
Okay, we're both naked
under these sheets here,

08:17.814 --> 08:19.380
you don't have to make that face
to let me know

08:19.381 --> 08:21.114
you're not excited.

08:24.048 --> 08:25.113
Diana, I can't.

08:25.114 --> 08:27.213
Yes, you can. You just have to want to.

08:27.214 --> 08:29.780
You just have to go into TAC
and clear up your schedule

08:29.781 --> 08:32.078
because this is more important.

08:32.748 --> 08:34.179
I'm more important.

08:34.181 --> 08:36.113
I've already signed with the other side.

08:36.582 --> 08:38.248
I'm working with the Clayton estate.

08:40.780 --> 08:41.847
Quit.

08:41.847 --> 08:43.547
I can't.

08:43.548 --> 08:45.947
And even if I wanted to,
I can't switch sides.

08:45.948 --> 08:47.313
It's a violation of professional ethics.

08:47.314 --> 08:48.514
You know that.

08:49.448 --> 08:51.914
I'm sorry.

09:05.881 --> 09:08.780
Will I see you again
while you're still in town?

09:08.781 --> 09:09.980
Absolutely.

09:10.450 --> 09:12.714
In court, Goliath.

09:16.348 --> 09:17.780
I'm really sorry.

09:17.781 --> 09:19.376
Then quit.

